      • filteredMappedJoin

        DataSet filteredMappedJoin(VTLDataSetMetadata metadata,
                           DataSet other,
                           BiPredicate<DataPoint,DataPoint> filter,
                           BinaryOperator<DataPoint> merge)
        Creates a new DataSet by joining DataPoints of this and another DataSet by the common identifiers.
        Parameters:
        metadata - The structure the new DataSet must conform to.
        other - another DataSet that will be joined to this DataSet.
        filter - a BiPredicate used to select only a subset of the joined DataPoints.
        merge - a BinaryOperator that merges two selected joined DataPoints together into one.
        Returns:
        The new DataSet.

      • filteredMappedJoin

        default DataSet filteredMappedJoin(VTLDataSetMetadata metadata,
                                   DataSet other,
                                   BinaryOperator<DataPoint> merge)
        Creates a new DataSet by joining DataPoints of this and another DataSet by the common identifiers. The same as filteredMappedJoin(metadata, other, (a, b) -> true, merge).
        Parameters:
        metadata - The structure the new DataSet must conform to.
        other - another DataSet that will be joined to this DataSet.
        merge - a BinaryOperator that merges two selected joined DataPoints together into one.
        Returns:
        The new DataSet.

      • streamByKeys

        <T> Stream<T> streamByKeys(Set<DataStructureComponent<ComponentRole.Identifier,?,?>> keys,
                           Map<DataStructureComponent<ComponentRole.Identifier,?,?>,ScalarValue<?,?,?>> filter,
                           BiFunction<? super Map<DataStructureComponent<ComponentRole.Identifier,?,?>,ScalarValue<?,?,?>>,? super Stream<DataPoint>,T> groupMapper)
        Perform a computation on each of the groups of the DataPoints of this DataSet which have the same value for each of (a subset of) its ComponentRole.Identifiers.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the result of the computation.
        Parameters:
        keys - the ComponentRole.Identifiers used to group the keys.
        filter - a Map containing values for some of this DataSet ComponentRole.Identifiers. The map will be used to filter out groups from the final computation.
        groupMapper - a BiFunction applied to each group to produce the final result
        Returns:
        a Stream of <T> objects containing the result of the computation for each group.

      • streamByKeys

        default <T> Stream<T> streamByKeys(Set<DataStructureComponent<ComponentRole.Identifier,?,?>> keys,
                                   BiFunction<? super Map<DataStructureComponent<ComponentRole.Identifier,?,?>,ScalarValue<?,?,?>>,? super Stream<DataPoint>,T> groupMapper)
        Perform a computation on each of the groups of the DataPoints of this DataSet which have the same value for each of (a subset of) its ComponentRole.Identifiers. The same as streamByKeys(keys, Collections.emptyMap(), groupMapper).
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the result of the computation.
        Parameters:
        keys - the ComponentRole.Identifiers used to group the keys.
        groupMapper - a BiFunction applied to each group to produce the final result
        Returns:
        a Stream of <T> objects containing the result of the computation for each group.
